INSTALL file for Brzdm

1. Prerequisites:
 - cmake
 - X.org or XFree86
 - libxmu
 - libpng
 - libjpeg
 - imlib2
 - nettle (upcoming version)
 - keyutils (upcoming version)
 - consolekit2

2. Defines:
 - setenv ARCH and MARCH of your computer, if not i486.
 - USE_CONSOLEKIT to enable CONSOLEKIT support.
 - USE_BRZDM_UID to enable brzdm uid support.
 - USE_KEYUTILS to enable keyring support.

3. to build and install the program:
 - edit the Makefile to adjust libraries and paths to your OS (if needed)
 - mkdir build ; cd build ; cmake ${optional-defines} ..
 - make && make install
 
4. automatic startup
 - Edit the init scripts according to your OS/Distribution.

